  <brief_title>Natriuretic Peptides After Left Atrial Appendage Amputation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of Left Atrial Appendage Amputation on Natriuretic Peptides - a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
